collatz steps of start: i32 gives i32:
  track n: i32 from start
  track steps: i32 from 0
  while n is greater than 1:
    if n remainder 2 is equal to 0:
      n becomes n divided by 2
    otherwise:
      n becomes n times 3 plus 1
    steps becomes steps plus 1
  steps

main gives i32:
  collatz steps of 7
